<p>本文作者为<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6167306&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608441731" alt="Meltyland Nightmare" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6167306)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/meltyland-nightmare" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6167306); return false;">Meltyland Nightmare</a></span>。该作者的更多作品见<a href="/erwin-schrodinger-s-personnel-files">首席研究员祖绫的人事页。</a></p>
